@startuml

title Marketplace Post Listing and Filtering Sequence Diagram

actor User

participant "Frontend (Website)" as FE
participant "Apache\n(HTTP Server)" as Apache

box "Laravel Application" #LightGreen
  participant "Middleware" as MW
  participant "PostController" as PC
  participant "Eloquent ORM" as ORM
end box

database "MariaDB Database" as DB

note right of User
It is assumed the User is
authenticated/authorized unless an exception occurs.
end note


== Open Marketplace Page ==

User -> FE: Open Kinemarket page
activate User
activate FE
activate Apache
activate MW
activate PC
activate ORM
activate DB

FE -> Apache: GET /kinemarket

alt Route exists
    Apache -> MW: Forward HTTP marketplace page request
else Route not found
    Apache --> FE: 404 Not Found
    FE --> User: Display "Marketplace route not found" error
end

alt Valid + Authorized
    MW -> PC: Pass authenticated and authorized marketplace page request
else Validation/Auth error
    MW --> FE: 401 Unauthorized / 403 Forbidden
    FE --> User: Display validation or authorization error
end

PC -> ORM: Post::latest()->get()
ORM -> DB: SELECT * FROM posts ORDER BY created_at DESC

alt Initial page query success
    DB --> ORM: Post result set
    ORM --> PC: posts collection
    PC --> FE: Return kinemarket view
    FE --> User: Display marketplace page
else Initial page query failure
    DB --> ORM: Query failed / SQL exception
    ORM --> PC: Post retrieval failed
    PC --> FE: 500 Internal Server Error
    FE --> User: Display system error while loading marketplace
end


== Load Marketplace Posts ==

FE -> Apache: GET /posts

alt Route exists
    Apache -> MW: Forward HTTP marketplace posts request
else Route not found
    Apache --> FE: 404 Not Found
    FE --> User: Display "Marketplace posts route not found" error
end

alt Valid + Authorized
    MW -> PC: Pass authenticated and authorized marketplace posts request
else Validation/Auth error
    MW --> FE: 401 Unauthorized / 403 Forbidden
    FE --> User: Display validation or authorization error
end

PC -> ORM: Post::with('user')->latest()->get()
ORM -> DB: SELECT posts with related user ORDER BY created_at DESC

alt Posts query success
    DB --> ORM: Posts with seller records
    ORM --> PC: posts collection
else Posts query failure
    DB --> ORM: Query failed / SQL exception
    ORM --> PC: Marketplace post retrieval failed
    PC --> FE: 500 Internal Server Error
    FE --> User: Display system error while loading marketplace posts
end

loop For each post
    PC -> ORM: Review::where(seller_id = post.user_id)->avg('rating')
    ORM -> DB: SELECT AVG(rating) FROM reviews WHERE seller_id = ?

    PC -> ORM: Review::where(seller_id = post.user_id)->count()
    ORM -> DB: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM reviews WHERE seller_id = ?

    alt Review aggregate success
        DB --> ORM: Average rating and reviews count
        ORM --> PC: Seller review metrics retrieved
    else Review aggregate failure
        DB --> ORM: Query failed / SQL exception
        ORM --> PC: Seller review aggregate retrieval failed
        PC --> FE: 500 Internal Server Error
        FE --> User: Display system error while loading seller ratings
    end
end

PC --> FE: Return marketplace posts JSON
FE --> User: Display marketplace listings with seller name, rating, category, condition, price, and time posted


== Apply Marketplace Filters ==

User -> FE: Search posts or change category/rating/price/condition filters

alt Matching posts found
    FE --> User: Display filtered marketplace results
else No matching posts found
    FE --> User: Display "No se encontraron publicaciones."
end

@enduml